high_descs: Turn around and locate the stove.
Pick up the apple from the rear of the counter.
Carry the apple and turn around to find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside. Shut the door then open it again and take out the apple.
Hold the apple and move a step to the right to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside. Shut the door.
Turn around, move to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around, bring the apple to the microwave on the counter.
Heat the apple in the mike.
Bring the heated apple to the fridge on the right.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your left and head towards the sink, make a left at the sink and go to the counter to the right of the stove, straight ahead of you.
Pick up the apple, between the stove and the toaster, on the back of the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave, on the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the apple from the microwave.
Go to the refrigerator, directly to your right.
Place the apple in the refrigerator, on the second shelf, to the right of the green cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple in the refrigerator.
